name: Search a text using search box

testSteps.description: 1: Search a text using search box ({Name=abc, Description=123@##, Team=QA, Task=Learning, InvalidText=mnop, ValidText=abc})

children.description: Given Navigate to MIS Beta Application
Launch MIS beta
And Login to MIS with credentials "amisha.srivastava" "Gemini@123"
Login to MIS: amisha.srivastava, Gemini@123
Then Open "Manage Task Template" page of "TimeSheet" module
Navigate to page: Manage Task Template, TimeSheet
And Verify "Manage Task Template" page of type "Sub"
Verify page: Manage Task Template, Sub
And Add a new valid task template with "abc" "123@##" "QA" "Learning"
Click delete template: abc
Verify and accept confirmation
Click add new template
Add valid template: abc, 123@##, QA, Learning
And Perform invalid search for "mnop" using search box when records are displayed
Search text for non matching records: mnop
And Perform valid search for "abc" using search box when records are displayed
Search text for matching records: abc
Then Logout from MIS
Opt user menu action: Logout
